      • applyStrategies

        public void applyStrategies()
        Description copied from interface: Traversal.Admin
        Apply the registered TraversalStrategies to the traversal. Once the strategies are applied, the traversal is "locked" and can no longer have steps added to it. The order of operations for strategy applications should be: globally id steps, apply strategies to root traversal, then to nested traversals.
        Specified by:
        applyStrategies in interface Traversal.Admin<S,E>
